SVC frame format for daemon

- sessionID : 4 byte (00 00 00 00 for SVC_CMD_REGISTER_APP)
- data type: 1 byte
	+ 0: data packet
	+ 1: command packet

- data packet structure
	+ encrypted: 3th bit
	  using tcp: 2th bit
	  priority: 1&0 th bit
	
	+ svc appID: 4 byte
	+ data length: 4 byte
	+ data payload
	
- command packet structure
	+ command id: 1 byte
		° SVC_CMD_CHECK_ALIVE: check if the socket is still listened by app
			- daemon to client: 0 argument	
		° SVC_CMD_REGISTER_APP: resgister app to daemons
			- client to daemon : 2 argument: [(4 byte - appID), (4 byte - session secret)]
			- daemon to client: 2 argument: [(n byte - sessionID), (4 byte - the same session secret)]
		° SVC_CMD_CONNECT_STEP1:
			- client to daemon: 3 argument: [(1 byte - isClient = 0), (4 byte - address), (n bytes - challenge)]
			- daemon to daemon: 
			- server: 1 argument: [(1 byte - isServer = 1)]
	+ number of arguments: 1 byte
	+ [arguments' lengths in 2 bytes followed by arguments]
	
